here,min is used to find the numbers which is having least
max is used to find in numbers which is having highest
average is used to average all the numbers and divide by its total that also can be done by mysql.
eg:-
SELECT NAME,CITY,MAX(SALARY) FROM EMPLOYEE WHERE ....
2.SELECT NAME,CITY,MIN(REG_NO) FROM EMPLOYEE 
3.SELECT  AVG(SALARY) FROM EMPLOYEE;


